issue.title: Useage of Gas Station Network
issue.body:
## Current Situation
Users have to have Ether in their wallet to interact with the contract.

## Desired Feature
Contract should be able to be used without Ether by
- [ ] Event organisers
- [x] Users
- [x] Bouncers (are typically employed by event organiser)

## Solution Approach
https://docs.openzeppelin.com/contracts/2.x/gsn

issue.title: Upgradeable factory and event contracts
issue.body:
## Current Situation
Contract cannot be updated and need to be redeployed after adding new features and logic.

## Desired Feature
Factory contract should be upgradable (open-zeppelin and/or by own proxy).
